Package: sparseNumeric
Title: Sparse Numeric Vectors with S4 Methods
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Anjie", "Liu", email = "anjie.liu@utexas.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Provides an S4 class 'sparse_numeric' for representing numeric vectors
    in sparse form, along with methods for arithmetic, cross product,
    mean, Euclidean norm, and standardization, plus basic plotting and
    coercion to and from base R numeric vectors.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
